  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2980597/" class="title-link">跟着“启蒙”了一回</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2980597"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1540271/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1540271-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1540271/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">谷德</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-02-06"
      class="main-meta">2010-02-06 18:57:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2980597_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  传统文化中冠以“经”的内容，基本上希望人多读多诵多重视，最好能烂熟于心脱口而出。一般来说，研读这些书大多需要高深的知识背景。若有书千百年来习惯以“经”来称呼，正是突出其重要，而不是由“小和尚念经有口无心”的角度去看其流传广泛的一面。“小儿科、太极拳”都被误...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
